Text:
This is a worthless, 10-page pamphlet on how to create a fake dating profile to get to know women before approaching them with your real dating profile.

If you really need this, the original 118 KB  file is available if you sign up for a free 4shared account. (or just use bugmenot like I did)

I suspect that this is being repeatedly spammed to generate interest in the report. It's a scam. This torrent should be deleted.
